'''克氏症候群'''（{{lang-en|Klinefelter's syndrome}}）或称'''XXY'''、'''47XXY症候群'''，俗称'''次雄性'''症候群，是由於男性有两条或两条以上的[[X染色体|X染色体]]所致的疾病<ref name=NIH2013Def>{{cite web|title=Klinefelter Syndrome (KS): Overview|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/Pages/default.aspx|website=nichd.nih.gov|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2013-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318011309/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/Pages/default.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该疾病的主要特徵為[[男性不育|不孕]]<ref name=NIH2013Def/>。通常症状很轻微，甚至许多患者根本不知道他们患有该病<!-- <ref name=NIH2013Sym/> -->。

有些时候症状会非常显著，可能会出现肌肉虚弱、身高较高、[[运动协调|运动协调]]差、体毛稀少、[[外生殖器|外生殖器]]異常、缺乏性慾和嚴重的有[[男性女乳症|男性女乳症]] <ref name=NIH2013Sym/>。通常在[[青春期|青春期]]时发现克氏症候群的徵状<ref name=NIH2012Diag>{{cite web|title=How do health care providers diagnose Klinefelter syndrome (KS)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317010050/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。智力发展通常与一般人无异，但常见有[[阅读障碍|阅读障碍]]或是在说话上有困难<!-- <ref name=NIH2013Sym/> -->。若有超过三条X染色体，患者的症状会比较严重<ref name=NIH2013Sym>{{cite web|title=What are common symptoms of Klinefelter syndrome (KS)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402143647/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

克氏症候群的发病是隨机的<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Epi/> -->。随着孕妇年纪增大，怀有罹患此疾病的胎儿机会也逐渐提高<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Epi/> -->。这个疾病没有[[遗传|遗传性]]，所以不会由患病的父亲遗传给下一代<ref name=NIH2012Epi/>。这个疾病的原发机制是在原先就有Y染色体的前提下有一条以上的多余X染色体，患者体內的总[[染色体|染色体]]数目至少为47条甚至更多，无论如何，都较一般46条染色体为多<ref name = Vis2006 >{{cite journal | author = Visootsak J, Graham JM | title = Klinefelter syndrome and other sex chromosomal aneuploidies | journal = Orphanet Journal of Rare Diseases | volume = 1 | pages = 42 | year = 2006 | pmid = 17062147 | pmc = 1634840 | doi = 10.1186/1750-1172-1-42 | last2 = Graham Jr }}</ref>。克氏症候群能够藉著检测染色体[[核型|核型]]的[[基因检测|基因检测]]来获得確诊<ref name=NIH2012Diag/>。

虽然目前尚没有办法可以完全治癒克氏症候群，但有一些医学治疗对改善疾病有不小的帮助<ref name=NIH2012Prog/>。[[物理治疗|物理治疗]]、[[言语治疗|言语治疗]]、[[辅导|辅导]]，以及调整教学方法等可能有效<!-- <ref name=NIH2013Tx/> --> 。举例来说，[[物理治疗|物理治疗]]、[[言语治疗|言语治疗]]、[[心理辅导|心理辅导]]以及適当调整教学方法等等都能协助患者。{{le|睪固酮补充疗法|Androgen_replacement_therapy}}对於荷尔蒙严重不足或是低下的患者或有助益<!-- <ref name=NIH2013Tx/> -->。已经发育生成的乳房组织也可以藉由手术的方法移除<!-- <ref name=NIH2013Tx/> -->。约有一半的男性患者，藉由{{le|人工辅助生殖技术|Assisted_reproductive_technology}}的帮助有机会拥有自己的小孩，但是，这个是有相当的风险以及所费不貲<ref name=NIH2013Tx>{{cite web|title=What are the treatments for symptoms in Klinefelter syndrome (KS)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315093521/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。患者得乳癌的机率偏高，但仍低於女性得乳癌的机率<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brinton|first1=LA|title=Breast cancer risk among patients with Klinefelter syndrome.|journal=Acta paediatrica (Oslo, Norway : 1992)|date=June 2011|volume=100|issue=6|pages=814-8|pmid=21241366}}</ref>。此外，克氏症候群病患本身的平均寿命无异於一般人<ref name=NIH2012Prog>{{cite web|title=Is there a cure for Klinefelter syndrome (KS)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/cure.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317020352/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/cure.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

克氏症候群是一种常见的{{le|染色体异常疾病|chromosomal disorders}}，在新生男童中的发生率介於1/500到1/1000之间<ref name=NIH2012Epi>{{cite web|title=How many people are affected by or at risk for Klinefelter syndrome (KS)?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317020356/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Klinefelter syndrome | work = Genetics Home Reference | publisher = [[美国国家医学图书馆|National Library of Medicine]] | date = 2012-10-30 | url = http://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/klinefelter-syndrome | accessdate = 2012-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121115102919/http://ghr.nlm.nih.gov/condition/klinefelter-syndrome | archive-date = 2012-11-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该疾病是以它的发现者{{le|哈利·克林菲尔德|Harry Klinefelter}}来命名，哈利在1940年代时確立此疾病特徵<ref name=NIH2013Over>{{cite web|title=Klinefelter Syndrome (KS): Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/Default.aspx|website=nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=15 March 2015|date=2013-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318011314/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/klinefelter/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並接著在1956年找到造成此疾病的多余X染色体<ref>{{cite book|last1=Odom|first1=Samuel L.|title=Handbook of developmental disabilities|date=2009|publisher=Guilford|location=New York|isbn=9781606232484|page=113|edition=Pbk.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=U4VpCKVomHkC&pg=PA113|access-date=2016-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013722/https://books.google.ca/books?id=U4VpCKVomHkC&pg=PA113|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。由於小老鼠也同样有可能罹患XXY症候群，这个特点让它们成为极佳的研究样本<ref>{{cite book|last1=Conn|first1=P. Michael|title=Animal models for the study of human disease|date=2013|publisher=Elsevier Science & Technology Books|location=San Diego|isbn=9780124159129|page=780|edition=First|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=dVLVLIV8rD0C&pg=PA780|access-date=2016-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304134928/https://books.google.ca/books?id=dVLVLIV8rD0C&pg=PA780|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

